# Generated for Codex file visibility.
#
# Codex (and some tooling) uses ignore files to decide which files are visible/searchable.
# This repo's `.gitignore` intentionally ignores things like `workers.jsonc`, `temp/`, and
# `artifacts/`, but the agent still needs to *recognize* those files to do its job.
#
# This `.ignore` file re-includes everything that `.gitignore` excludes.
# NOTE: Visibility is not permission — avoid reading/seeking secrets (e.g. `.env`) unless
# the task explicitly requires it.

!workers.jsonc
!temp/
!temp/**
!artifacts/
!artifacts/**
